window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It was supposed to be a summer we’d never forget. Instead, everything was stolen from me.</p> <p>The best friend who was more like a sister.<br> The innocent way I looked at life.<br> Leaving me with only unanswered questions.</p> <p>Returning to the island is the second chance I didn’t know I needed. And Hunter is the surprise that knocks me sideways.</p> <p>There’s a hurt in him that calls to my own.<br> A strength I find in sharing our scars.<br> Igniting a spark that turns to flame.</p> <p>But someone isn’t happy about the world I’m building for myself. And nothing will stop them from tearing it all apart....</p>"; 
